block contenido

        main
            section.nosotros
                .nosotros__text-container
                    h2 About us
                    p We are a firm of certified public accounts that has been operating since 1983 offering audit and assurance, tax advisory, business and financial consulting services, as well as accounting and organizational development services with high international quality standards. We are a firm incorporated in the Dominican Republic with a solid family base made up of highly qualified personnel and with an internal quality system based on international standards. Our firm is always ready to meet the needs and expectations of its clients.
            
            section.nosotrosVideo
                .nosotrosVideo__text
                    h2 We are members of BKR International, a leading global association of independent auditing and tax consulting firms.
                    p Being part of such a prestigious association ensures our effective cooperation across borders: 150 Firms associated with more than 580 offices in 81 countries around the world. BKR offers a combination of resources, methodologies, representation and local and international knowledge, as well as a global network experience. On this basis, our clients can access services that allow them to meet their needs throughout the country, region and around the world.
                
                .sobreNosotrosVideo__video.fade-in
                    iframe.video-iframe(src='https://player.vimeo.com/video/315315231?h=651cf7feaf' width='320' height='360' frameborder='0' allow='autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture' allowfullscreen='allow' title="Video de la empresa")


            section.nosotrosMV.fade-in
                .nosotrosMV__text
                    .nosotrosMV__text--1
                        h2 Mission
                        p Satisfy the needs and expectations of our clients by being their strategic adviser for solutions that contribute to their business and/or personal development through our commitment to provide them with personalized auditing, consulting, Tax Advisory and outsourcing services based on innovation and excellence.
                    .nosotrosMV__text--2
                        h2 Vision 
                        p To stand out among the firms with the greatest national and international recognition for the level of commitment and quality of the services we offer and the generation of value we create for our clients, associates, employees and society.
            
            section.nosotrosValores.fade-in
                .nosotrosValores__container
